==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subglottic
<hw>Sub*glot"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated below the glottis; -- applied to that part of the cavity
of the larynx below the true vocal cords.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subglumaceous</ent>⟦br⟧
